Simple way to disable Metro infrastructure



    Open regedit go to key
    Code:

    HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon
    Set EnableSIHostIntegration to 0

    Then install startisback, to have some of the disabled feature available again(like start menu, closing windows from taskbar)
    logoff to take effect

    Here how its impact the processes and handles
    trying to exec metro app wont work with error class not registered
